headline: Jefferies on internet stocks: Own names offering ’peer-leading EBITDA growth’
summary: Investing.com -- Jefferies told investors on Wednesday that they should focus on internet stocks with strong earnings visibility and standout EBITDA growth as the macro narrative fades into the background this quarter.

headline: Remain On The Sidelines, But Would Prefer Airbnb To Expedia

headline: 1 Volatile Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 to Brush Off
